my config files for suckless software
=====================================

Installation
------------
    Create a suckless folder (or anything u want) and run

        git clone https://github.com/lazarescu1/suckless.git
        cd suckless
        cd dwm && make clean install
        cd dmenu && make clean install
        cd slstatus && make clean install

Usage
-----
    Add 

        exec dwm &
        exec slstatus
    
    to your ~/.xinitrc file to run dwm and slstatus

    See

        https://dwm.suckless.org/
        https://dmenu.suckless.org/
        https://slstatus.suckless.org/
    
    for more info
